00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:44.800
Apa kata itu?  Limbah..

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:46.600
Teruslah menyia-nyiakannya.

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:49.960
Di sisi lain, kakak
ipar telah memutuskan

00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:52.760
